'''Scharnhorst''' may refer to:

; Place name:
* [[Scharnhorst, Lower Saxony]], a municipality in the district of Celle, Lower Saxony, Germany
* Scharnhorst, {{link|de|Basse (Neustadt am R<U+00FC>benberge)}}
* {{link|de|Stadtbezirk Dortmund-Scharnhorst}}, [[Dortmund]]
:* {{link|de|Dortmund-Alt-Scharnhorst}}
* {{link|de|Scharnhorst (Verden)}}, [[Verden (Aller)]]

